Package br.com.parg.viacep

package br.com.parg.viacep
This package contains the classes for integration with the ViaCEP service.

The classes in this package are responsible for fetching CEP information through the ViaCEP service. The main class in this package is ViaCEP.

This package was originally created by Pablo Alexander (pablo@parg.com.br) and is available at https://viacep.com.br/.
